Wrong Place, Write Crime is a podcast about crime fiction authors, mysteries, art and life featuring Frank Zafiro as host. Episodes include guest interviews (primarily with authors of crime fiction, but not always), as well as quick hit reviews from mystery bookstore experts, flash interviews with future guests and updates on works in progress by the host and other authors. /  / This podcast explores the art of writing crime fiction, the art of reading crime fiction, and any other cool topic that comes up, as long as it falls under the category of either ‘art’ or ‘life.’
